# Settings restore twin: run on rung4_settings.scn's profile. A fresh process
# restores the sidecar's viewer override AND applies it — the boot respawn
# routes through the pinned engine, so the setting survives a restart as an
# applied fact, not a stored string.
settle 40
key escape
assert focused example.com
assert content-live
act Open Inspector pane
settle 5
assert row Viewer: genet.livery
assert row Engine: genet.livery
capture 01_livery_after_restart
log settings restore twin complete
